item.title: CVE-2018-7820|2024-08-05T06:37:59.195Z -- schneider%20electric%20se -- apc%20ups%20network%20management%20card%202%20aos
item.description: A Credentials Management CWE-255 vulnerability exists in the APC UPS Network Management Card 2 AOS v6.5.6, which could cause Remote Monitoring Credentials to be viewed in plaintext when Remote Monitoring is enabled, and then disabled.
